{{wikipediapar|Allahu Akbar}}
==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* [[Allah akbar]]

===Etymology===
From Arabic [[الله]] ([[Allah]]/[[God]]) and [[أكبر]] (’ákbar, [[greater]]/[[greatest]]), the [[elative]] ({{compar}}/{{superl}}) of [[كبير]] (kabí:r, [[big]]).

===Phrase===
'''[[Allahu]] [[akbar]]'''

# (''Islam'') The [[Muslim]] [[takbir]] ([[proclamation]]) "[[God]] is most [[great]]."

